            "title": "盤中速報 - 必治妥施貴寶(BMY-US)大跌5.01%，報46.2美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>必治妥施貴寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BMY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BMY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BMY-US</a>)截至台北時間14日23:02股價下跌2.44美元，報46.20美元，跌幅5.01%，成交量4,507,857（股），盤中最高價48.37美元、最低價46.19美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.17%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.62%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.56%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.23%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>必治妥施貴寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BMY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BMY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BMY-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.25%</li> <li>近 1 月：+12.72%</li> <li>近 3 月：+2.57%</li> <li>近 6 月：+5.34%</li> <li>今年以來：-13.58%</li></ul></section></main>",
